heading: Inupiaq dialect materials.
general-note: Here are entered works written in Inupiaq intended primarily for general information or recreational reading. Such works with text also given in English are further subdivided by the subdivision Bilingual, i.e.,. Inupiaq dialect materials--Bilingual.. Reading texts in Inupiaq containing material for instruction and practice in reading that dialect are entered under. Inupiaq dialect--Readers..
